metadata.description: In a world populated by the most fearsome thieves, murderers, and ne’er-do-wells, there is one who is a HEAD above the rest. Enter, M.O.D.O.K.: The Mental Organism Designed Only for Killing! Killville’s very own Merc with a Maw is open for business! But his next job may be biting off more than he can chew.
metadata.name: M.O.D.O.K. Assassin
